        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Humane Correctional Health Care Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows states to cover inmates of public institutions under Medicaid. The Government Accountability Office must report on specified information relating to the health of inmates and the effects of Medicaid coverage.</p>]]>
        </text>
